These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, argentine, indonesian
1. the japanese is in an odd position##4
2. the indonesian is between the chinese and the japanese##2
3. the indonesian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | chinese | indonesian | japanese | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, tomato, peach, cabbage
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pear | cabbage | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, western, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching thriller movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | sports | western | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, golf, skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | golf | water-polo | skateboarding | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, parkour, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | skateboarding | cycling | parkour | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, russian, dutch
1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left or right of the dutch##3
3. the russian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | russian | nigerian | dutch | pakistani |

