.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, gospel, electronic
1. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the fan of jazz is between the fan of r&b and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | r&b | jazz | gospel |

