2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | fishing | rock-climbing | skydiving | video-games |

