1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching crime movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | documentary | family | sports |

