.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, airplane, tram, ship
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | airplane | ship | train |

