.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, soy-milk, sprite
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk | coffee | sprite |

