3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | swimming | parkour | water-polo | skateboarding |

