.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, kale, corn, cherry
1. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating raspberry is in an even position##4
5. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | corn | cherry | kale | raspberry |

